# Copy to `.env.local` (or merge with the repo root `.env` as you prefer).

# Must match **`api`** `JWT_SECRET` (HS256 session + OTP). Used by **`src/middleware.ts`** to verify cookies.
# JWT_SECRET=

# Go API base URL (no trailing slash), **browser only** — when set, **`getApiRoute()`** returns absolute URLs
# and **`next.config.ts`** disables rewrites (use with **`CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS`** on the API).
# When **unset**, **`getApiRoute()`** stays same-origin (`/api/...`) and Next rewrites forward to the Go API
# (`API_ORIGIN` / default `http://127.0.0.1:8080`) so the session cookie remains on the Next origin for **`middleware.ts`**.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:8080

# Server-only (SSR, Server Actions): preferred over **`NEXT_PUBLIC_API_ORIGIN`** for **`getApiOrigin()`** on the server (e.g. Docker: `http://api:8080`).
# API_ORIGIN=
